        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nHi Liu,\nthe patch looks good, but the Security checks show, that the intent pod runs as root:\nhttps://logs.onap.org/onap-integration/gating//134897-3/root_pods/root_pods/root_pods.log\n```\nPOD: onap-uui-intent-analysis-58c5d94b7f-flrpw container: uui-intent-analysis uid: 0(root)\n```\nThis is usually not allowed and the SECCOM will recognize this as a fault.\nIf it has to run as root, a waiver has to be requested\n\nBest regards\nAndreas",
